43. What is the purpose of the `@aws-cdk/aws-lambda` library in AWS CDK?
44. How can you define and manage Amazon RDS (Relational Database Service) in AWS CDK?
45. What is the AWS CDK Pipelines and how is it used in CI/CD?
46. How do you configure AWS CDK applications for different deployment environments (e.g., dev, test, prod)?
47. What is the role of the `cdk bootstrap` command in an AWS CDK project?
48. How do you handle resource deletion and cleanup in AWS CDK applications?
49. Can you provide an example of creating a simple AWS CDK application using TypeScript?
50. What are some best practices for developing and maintaining AWS CDK applications in TypeScript?
